---
title: One-Pot Hearty Lentil Soup with Carrots, Celery, Kidney Beans & Sour Cream
description: This hearty vegetarian soup is packed with two types of plant-based protein—lentils and beans—and loads of veggies. Tender lentils simmer with carrots, celery, and onion in a delicately spiced vegetable broth, and kidney beans add body and richness. Serve with a dollop of sour cream and chopped chives for a final flourish.
